 them in there, but they're still loose so I obviously didn't seat them 
 correctly. Is it okay to hold something up that matches the outside edge 
 of the tube, such as some PVC pipe and bang on that to seat them? I'm 
 afraid it could rip the O-Ring seals going into the case. 
